  "comment": "BTS300Z LED Profile Spot Zoom 300W Warm White: The BTS300Z is a 300W COB high power LED profile spot with manual zoom. The zoom range can be set from 18° to 36° and covers the most regular 19°, 26°, 36° lenses. It features a HQ optical system, a strong ABS housing and an ultra-low power consumption with a surprising output thanks to the 300W LED power source. With this high output LED engine that has near silent cooling it can be used in theatre, studio and concert venues of all types. \n\n",
